{"tid":2499361,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"邦民女都搞選舉 ⊙.⊙","createTime":"2021-04-22T00:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T00:56:53.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"932625f91ee1dfd0988feb0753e5ac04249e4ee9","tid":2499361,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T00:07:10.000Z","msg":"邦民日本財務歷年捧出不少「邦民女」女神，包括第一代的梁寶琪(Crystal)、第二代羅凱珊(Kama)、第三代陳嘉寶(Anjaylia)、第四代黎紀君(Christy Lai)及第五代的鄺潔楹。近日邦民決定由民選方式，舉辦《邦民人氣選 : 女神練習生》選舉，由市民自己一人一票選出心中邦民女。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RmilbtHH89E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRmilbtHH89E&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=f83f5471\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RmilbtHH89E</a>"},{"pid":"874cfa712f7177372e1d852ae52dac2acacec6d0","tid":2499361,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T00:07:22.000Z","msg":"新一代邦民大使即將誕生，今次選拔仲可以全民參與，市民可到 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/3abg6Si\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3abg6Si&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=2c1aed4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3abg6Si</a> 投票給心目中的女神，及留意ViuTV 99台《邦民人氣選：女神練習生》的播出時間，而4位候選「邦民女」練習生：Angel、Carrie、Eunice同Kate已經準備就緒，施展渾身解數，爭取成為新一代邦民女。"},{"pid":"4d80b3443b8f44a4204828f76b9c64938247e1e7","tid":2499361,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T00:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/7xzCTnbJ7adXKVpj9goa9ITg7DXNxE4p7r-4k5f5eb_tF2um0cNmZ4aH4aLNZXhtIN0bxj2u1ZDg8iFyh4PP2pL6Pe2hsTvXVY9XZJHrozBP1V_cHsplNEBtW-lsYbjuhA=w260\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F7xzCTnbJ7adXKVpj9goa9ITg7DXNxE4p7r-4k5f5eb_tF2um0cNmZ4aH4aLNZXhtIN0bxj2u1ZDg8iFyh4PP2pL6Pe2hsTvXVY9XZJHrozBP1V_cHsplNEBtW-lsYbjuhA%3Dw260&h=783c9bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/hm3gdNnApVBLT2N2H7jmQC2OSArQ_NR_8iagI-ARjy90cqYg7hNMVEkwZWHDaP